Package preprocess.tokenize

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Tokenizer
    The Tokenizer creates Submissions from a path.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeneralTokenizer
    The Tokenizer iterates through a directory specified by a Path and returns all submissions Submission matching the SubmissionStructure.
    Submission
    The class representing a submission, it is passed around during processing.
    SubmissionStructure
    Holds the structure of a submission, i.e. how directories are organized etc.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidStructureException
    Indicates that the SubmissionStructure object is not valid.
    MaximumDirectoryDepthExceededException
    Indicates that the Directory structure parsed by the Tokenizer exceeded the depth limit specified in the Tokenizer.
